1、/give @p minecraft:bow 1 0 {Unbreakable:1b}
/give @p minecraft:bow 1 1 {Unbreakable:1b}
/give @p minecraft:bow 1 2 {Unbreakable:1b}
/give @p minecraft:bow 1 3 {Unbreakable:1b}
弓的物品只有这四种材质，/give @p minecraft:bow 1 4 {Unbreakable:1b}材质就丢失了
2、http://www.mcbbs.net/thread-510037-1-1.html
3、右键探测很难，如果硬要探测就探测空地图使用（因为使用后会变成地图，然后探测地图就好了）
4、/scoreboard objectives add arrow dummy
/scoreboard players set @e[type=Arrow] arrow 1
/execute @e[type=Arrow] ~ ~ ~ detect ~ ~-1 ~ air 0 scoreboard set @e[type=Arrow,r=0] arrow 0
用/testfor @e[score_arrow_min=1]即可探测
